{
  "version": "2.6.2",
  "summary": {
    "title": " User Authentication System",
    "owner": "Mudassir ",
    "description": "- DFD: User -> Web Server -> Session Manager -> User Database.\n- Threats:\n  1. Spoofing: Credential stuffing on login. Mitigation: MFA, Rate limiting.\n  2. Tampering: Session token manipulation. Mitigation: Signed/Encrypted tokens.\n  3. Information Disclosure: Plaintext passwords in DB. Mitigation: Argon2 hashing.\n  4. Denial of Service: Brute force exhausting resources. Mitigation: Account lockout.",
    "id": 0
  },
